  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "First of all, we would like to start with initialising Spark environment by specifying the full path to the Spark installation,enabling us to use PySpark in our notebook. Additionally, we added the exception handling with try/except block to ensure that any errors during initialization are caught and handled in timely manner, as the path might differ depending on the user's environment."
