  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "As the next step, we initialize a local PySpark environment with a SparkSession named \"FakeNewsDataSet_Preprocessing\" and allocate 2 GB executor memory. As well, we prepare both SparkContext and SQLContext for distributed data processing."
