  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Now we want to assess the balance of class labels to ensure that both categories are well represented. First, we group the data by the label column and count the number of records for each class.\n",
    "Then, we plot a bar chart showing the distribution of samples for each class label."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 45,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
