   "source": [
    "As we can see, after trimming whitespace and filtering out rows with null or empty \"text\" values, the remaining dataset has 44,058 rows. Now, we will check if the language in the \"text\" column is English using the previously defined udf **check_lang_udf**. Additionally, we cache the resulting DataFrame to optimize performance for subsequent operations by avoiding repeated computations."
