  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "As the next step, we create a new column \"stop_text\" by applying the **remove_stops_udf** to the \"text\" column, which removes English stopwords from the text. The resulting DataFrame is also cached to optimize performance for future operations that use this processed data."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 54,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
